@node description "What is MoreText?"

MoreText is a powerful, yet easy to use text / AmigaGuide viewer.
It uses standard IO, so it's ideal for BBS usage. Of course it works
fine on shell too.

Viewing of AmigaGuides is very easy : use TAB to move to the next
link and RETURN to jump to a new node. Link jumps can be naturally
retraced. Also INDEX node is supported.

MoreText supports XPK system (crypting algorithms too) with
both texts and AmigaGuides.

Other features include fast search and line jump routines etc...

@endnode

